On 19th March, 1575, Mr. John Skene was admitted advocate; and, in 1577, he married Helen Somerville, eldest daughter of Sir John Somerville of Camnethan by his second wife, Catherine, daughter of John Murray of Falahill; her sister, Dame N icolas Somerville, being wife ol Walter, Lord Blantyre.
